, as you make music magic in this VR-exclusive experience featuring 40-plus songs from 50 top artists across EDM, hip hop, trap, and countless other genres.\nMusic Reality Engine\u2122: Electronauts\u2019 proprietary technology always keeps your sounds bumpin\u2019 on beat, no matter how much you mix.\nExperiment: Record loops and sequences, layer filters, mashup and arrange songs to your style as you make them your own.\nPerform: Crush your set with surreal visuals, adaptable colors, and dynamic camera angles that make your performance fit your mood.", "short_description": "Ever wanted to ride the vibes of a top DJ playing a packed festival\u2019s main stage? Here\u2019s your chance to shine: all it takes to be an Electronaut is the passion to become one with the beat. Create music with confidence, no matter your skill level, as you make music magic in this VR-exclusive experience featuring 40-plus songs from 50 top artists across EDM, hip hop, trap, and countless other genres."}]}, "developer_name": "Survios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.electronautsvr.com/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.electronautsvr.com/", "publisher_name": "Survios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.electronautsvr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1819021644882647"}, {"id": "726368587961803"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "MUSIC", "ART_CREATIVITY"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "en_US"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SIN